<title>ḍạqt ʿly ạlkrwb</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ḍạqt ʿly ạlkrwb wlạ gẖyrk hạyfrjhạ ạ̹nt ạ̹lhy ạlmhmwb ʿạrf mkẖạrjhạ
 mtʿlq ạ̉nạ byk wnjạty byn ạ̹ydyk fy ạ̹smk ạḥtmy wkl ạ̹tkạly ʿlyk
 fy qdsk ạlkrym tftḥ bṣyrẗ qlby wạlfkr yʿwd slym yhrb tnhydy wtʿby
 wạ̹n hạj ạlbḥr ʿly tyjy mạsẖy ʿ ạlmyh wtḥwl ạlạ̉zmạt lmʿjzạt smạwyẗ
 ʿdwy tẖạyr qwy lkn ạ̹ydyk sạndạny wạḥḍạnk btḥtwy ḍʿfy wqlh ạ̹ymạny
 wạblys yạkẖd wsạwsh wtrjʿ tʿyyrh lnfsh mktwb ạlly ykẖạf ạlrb mlạk ạlrb ḥạrsh</lyrics>
</song>